{"uid":"7c3c948c0e31e70b","name":"test_leader_change_and_restart","fullName":"tests.integration.test_persistent_temp_storage_restart#test_leader_change_and_restart","historyId":"35deb2ff536d995cc57214e6e1b0c44f","time":{},"description":"Force leader change and restart to trigger the library fix code path.\n\n    This test properly validates the fix from\n    https://github.com/canonical/postgresql-single-kernel-library/pull/54 by:\n    1. Finding the current Juju leader\n    2. Killing the leader's juju agent to force leader election\n    3. Waiting for a new leader to be elected\n    4. Restarting the new leader's LXD machine\n    5. Verifying the log message appears confirming the fix handled persistent temp storage\n\n    This scenario triggers set_up_database() on the new leader during the start event,\n    which should detect the persistent temp storage and log the appropriate message.\n    ","descriptionHtml":"<p>Force leader change and restart to trigger the library fix code path.</p>\n<pre><code>This test properly validates the fix from\nhttps://github.com/canonical/postgresql-single-kernel-library/pull/54 by:\n1. Finding the current Juju leader\n2. Killing the leader's juju agent to force leader election\n3. Waiting for a new leader to be elected\n4. Restarting the new leader's LXD machine\n5. Verifying the log message appears confirming the fix handled persistent temp storage\n\nThis scenario triggers set_up_database() on the new leader during the start event,\nwhich should detect the persistent temp storage and log the appropriate message.\n</code></pre>\n","status":"unknown","flaky":false,"newFailed":false,"newBroken":false,"newPassed":false,"retriesCount":0,"retriesStatusChange":false,"beforeStages":[],"afterStages":[],"labels":[{"name":"parentSuite","value":"tests.integration"},{"name":"suite","value":"test_persistent_temp_storage_restart"},{"name":"host","value":"runnervm35a4x"},{"name":"framework","value":"pytest"},{"name":"language","value":"cpython